data.description: Great Starter/Investor Home, Walking Distance to the Colorado River and the Amazing Rotary Park that Offers a Boat Launch, Skate Park, Playground, Walking Trails, Beach and much, much more.  3 Bedrooms, 2 Bathrooms and a 2 Car Attached Finished Garage.  Kitchen Offers a large Pantry, Range with Double Oven and Refrigerator.  Recently Replaced Kitchen Sink, Water Heater and Garage Door Opener.   Back Yard of Home has Chainlink Fencing. Centrally Located, Close to Shopping, Medical and all the Fun and excitement of Laughlin NV.
